The remaining jets studied by Karlsson et al. (2018) consisted of ion populations similar to, but cooler than, the surrounding magnetosheath. Three of the jets exhibited isotropic temperature, while one exhibited anisotropy \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
