				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\,R_{\mathrm{E}}$\end{document}RE. These true scale sizes are significantly smaller than the median observed scale sizes: 0.89\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
