A comparison of the results of Goncharov et al. (2020) and Plaschke et al. (2020a) shows that in both studies the jets are more elongated in the direction parallel to the flow. The median observed scale sizes are also similar in both studies: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
